00:04:43.714 --> 00:04:45.921
Tapi jangan datang ke sini lain kali.

00:04:46.589 --> 00:04:48.630
Pergi sekarang.  Anak baik.

00:04:51.880 --> 00:04:54.630
Kamu tidak kenal Sunny.
Dia sangat keras kepala, Prisha.

00:04:55.255 --> 00:04:57.088
